works.description: We have recently told you about the chromed Audi R8 Spyder that went up for auction to benefit Elton John’s charity foundation. The chromed Audi finally has been auctioned at the 13th edition of Sir Elton John’s White Tie and Tiara Ball event this year for a price of $400k. The event was held at famous music superstar, Sir Elton John’s home along with his partner David Furnish.
